\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 支持rich text，<strong>bold </strong><em>italic</em><strong> </strong><ins><strong>underline</strong></ins><strong> </strong><del><strong>strike</strong></del><br />\n- rich text 支持 predefined hotkey<br />\n- 支持quote，code，加密<br />\n- 未支持上載image，用返連登嗰個先<br />\n- 打完一鍵copy，去連登paste搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- Auto save，自動記住你上次打過嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，data儲喺client side<br />\n- 唔收集任何user data，無backend server，offline都行到嘅tool<br />\n- 支持standalone網頁版面 同埋 chrome extension<br />\n- 支持開關<code>透明版面</code><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">Chrome Extension</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span><a href=\"https://dwomeco2.github.io/lihkg_wysiwyg_editor/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdwomeco2.github.io%2Flihkg_wysiwyg_editor%2F&d=TRt9Hu9y5T%2Bqj71zgJeH9j632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=4ef9ca5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://dwomeco2.github.io/lihkg_wysiwyg_editor/</a><span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">SHA-256: </span><code>df8f717c1666df29b476e5f9fad8cd20c56014cffdb422d88fa5fe618adcfee5</code></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> </span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">網頁版傳送門</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span><a href=\"https://lihkg-wysiwyg-editor.surge.sh/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flihkg-wysiwyg-editor.surge.sh%2F&d=TRt9Hu9y5T%2Bqj71zgJeH9j632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=ed7d2bc2\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg-wysiwyg